The paper deals with unsupervised anomaly detection, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper also introduces a new ensemble method that incorporates privileged information, which is a concept that falls under the umbrella of learning using privileged information (LUPI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these sub-categories are also relevant to the paper's content.
